{"message": "I'll create a modern landing page for a SaaS product with all the essential sections: navigation, hero, features, testimonials, pricing, and footer. The design will use a clean layout with the specified color scheme and responsive design principles.","design": {"id": "root", "type": "root", "tag": "div", "children": [{"id": "page", "type": "container", "tag": "div", "style": {"minHeight": "100vh", "display": "flex", "flexDirection": "column", "backgroundColor": "#ffffff"}}, {"id": "nav", "type": "nav", "tag": "nav", "style": {"display": "flex", "justifyContent": "space-between", "alignItems": "center", "padding": "16px 24px", "backgroundColor": "#ffffff", "borderBottom": "1px solid #e2e8f0", "position": "sticky", "top": "0", "zIndex": "100"}}, {"id": "nav-logo", "type": "link", "tag": "a", "style": {"fontSize": "24px", "fontWeight": "700", "color": "#10b981", "textDecoration": "none"}}, "SaaSPro"}, {"id": "nav-links", "type": "container", "tag": "div", "style": {"display": "flex", "gap": "24px"}}, {"id": "nav-link-1", "type": "link", "tag": "a", "style": {"color": "#475569", "textDecoration": "none", "fontWeight": "500", "transition": "color 0.2s"}}, "Features"}, {"id": "nav-link-2", "type": "link", "tag": "a", "style": {"color": "#475569", "textDecoration": "none", "fontWeight": "500", "transition": "color 0.2s"}}, "Pricing"}, {"id": "nav-link-3", "type": "link", "tag": "a", "style": {"color": "#475569", "textDecoration": "none", "fontWeight": "500", "transition": "color 0.2s"}}, "Contact"}, {"id": "nav-button", "type": "button", "tag": "button", "style": {"backgroundColor": "#10b981", "color": "#ffffff", "border": "none", "padding": "10px 20px", "borderRadius": "6px", "fontWeight": "600", "cursor": "pointer", "transition": "background-color 0.2s"}}, "Get Started"}, {"id": "hero", "type": "section", "tag": "section", "style": {"padding": "80px 24px", "textAlign": "center", "backgroundColor": "#f8fafc"}}, {"id": "hero-content", "type": "container", "tag": "div", "style": {"maxWidth": "800px", "margin": "0 auto"}}, {"id": "hero-heading", "type": "heading", "tag": "h1", "style": {"fontSize": "48px", "fontWeight": "800", "color": "#0f172a", "marginBottom": "24px", "lineHeight": "1.2"}}, "Transform Your Business with Powerful SaaS Solutions"}, {"id": "hero-subheading", "type": "text", "tag": "p", "style": {"fontSize": "20px", "color": "#475569", "marginBottom": "32px", "lineHeight": "1.6"}}, "Streamline your operations, boost productivity, and drive growth with our comprehensive SaaS platform designed for modern businesses."}, {"id": "hero-buttons", "type": "container", "tag": "div", "style": {"display": "flex", "justifyContent": "center", "gap": "16px", "flexWrap": "wrap"}}, {"id": "hero-primary-btn", "type": "button", "tag": "button", "style": {"backgroundColor": "#10b981", "color": "#ffffff", "border": "none", "padding": "14px 28px", "borderRadius": "8px", "fontSize": "18px", "fontWeight": "600", "cursor": "pointer", "transition": "background-color 0.2s"}}, "Start Free Trial"}, {"id": "hero-secondary-btn", "type": "button", "tag": "button", "style": {"backgroundColor": "transparent", "color": "#10b981", "border": "2px solid #10b981", "padding": "14px 28px", "borderRadius": "8px", "fontSize": "18px", "fontWeight": "600", "cursor": "pointer", "transition": "all 0.2s"}}, "Watch Demo"}, {"id": "hero-image", "type": "image", "tag": "img", "style": {"width": "100%", "maxWidth": "800px", "height": "400px", "objectFit": "cover", "borderRadius": "12px", "marginTop": "48px"}}, {"src": "https://placehold.co/800x400/10b981/ffffff?text=SaaS+Dashboard"}, {"id": "features", "type": "section", "tag": "section", "style": {"padding": "80px 24px", "backgroundColor": "#ffffff"}}, {"id": "features-header", "type": "container", "tag": "div", "style": {"maxWidth": "800px", "margin": "0 auto 60px", "textAlign": "center"}}, {"id": "features-heading", "type": "heading", "tag": "h2", "style": {"fontSize": "36px", "fontWeight": "700", "color": "#0f172a", "marginBottom": "16px"}}, "Powerful Features for Modern Businesses"}, {"id": "features-subheading", "type": "text", "tag": "p", "style": {"fontSize": "18px", "color": "#475569", "lineHeight": "1.6"}}, "Everything you need to streamline your operations and drive growth."}, {"id": "features-grid", "type": "grid", "tag": "div", "style": {"display": "grid", "gridTemplateColumns": "repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr))", "gap": "32px"}}, {"id": "feature-1", "type": "card", "tag": "div", "style": {"backgroundColor": "#f8fafc", "borderRadius": "12px", "padding": "32px", "boxShadow": "0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)", "transition": "transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s"}}, {"id": "feature-icon-1", "type": "icon", "tag": "div", "style": {"width": "64px", "height": "64px", "backgroundColor": "#10b981", "borderRadius": "50%", "display": "flex", "alignItems": "center", "justifyContent": "center", "marginBottom": "20px", "color": "#ffffff", "fontSize": "28px"}}, "🚀"}, {"id": "feature-title-1", "type": "heading", "tag": "h3", "style": {"fontSize": "22px", "fontWeight": "600", "color": "#0f172a", "marginBottom": "12px"}}, "Lightning Fast Performance"}, {"id": "feature-desc-1", "type": "text", "tag": "p", "style": {"fontSize": "16px", "color": "#475569", "lineHeight": "1.6"}}, "Experience blazing-fast load times and seamless performance with our optimized infrastructure."}, {"id": "feature-2", "type": "card", "tag": "div", "style": {"backgroundColor": "#f8fafc", "borderRadius": "12px", "padding": "32px", "boxShadow": "0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)", "transition": "transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s"}}, {"id": "feature-icon-2", "type": "icon", "tag": "div", "style": {"width": "64px", "height": "64px", "backgroundColor": "#10b981", "borderRadius": "50%", "display": "flex", "alignItems": "center", "justifyContent": "center", "marginBottom": "20px", "color": "#ffffff", "fontSize": "28px"}}, "🔒"}, {"id": "feature-title-2", "type": "heading", "tag": "h3", "style": {"fontSize": "22px", "fontWeight": "600", "color": "#0f172a", "marginBottom": "12px"}}, "Enterprise Security"}, {"id": "feature-desc-2", "type": "text", "tag": "p", "style": {"fontSize": "16px", "color": "#475569", "lineHeight": "1.6"}}, "Bank-level encryption and compliance with industry standards to keep your data safe."}, {"id": "feature-3", "type": "card", "tag": "div", "style": {"backgroundColor": "#f8fafc", "borderRadius": "12px", "padding": "32px", "boxShadow": "0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)", "transition": "transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s"}}, {"id": "feature-icon-3", "type": "icon", "tag": "div", "style": {"width": "64px", "height": "64px", "backgroundColor": "#10b981", "borderRadius": "50%", "display": "flex", "alignItems": "center", "justifyContent": "center", "marginBottom": "20px", "color": "#ffffff", "fontSize": "28px"}}, "📊"}, {"id": "feature-title-3", "type": "heading", "tag": "h3", "style": {"fontSize": "22px", "fontWeight": "600", "color": "#0f172a", "marginBottom": "12px"}}, "Advanced Analytics"}, {"id": "feature-desc-3", "type": "text", "tag": "p", "style": {"fontSize": "16px", "color": "#475569", "lineHeight": "1.6"}}, "Gain valuable insights with powerful reporting tools and real-time data visualization."}, {"id": "testimonials", "type": "section", "tag": "section", "style": {"padding": "80px 24px", "backgroundColor": "#f8fafc"}}, {"id": "testimonials-header", "type": "container", "tag": "div", "style": {"maxWidth": "800px", "margin": "0 auto 60px", "textAlign": "center"}}, {"id": "testimonials-heading", "type": "heading", "tag": "h2", "style": {"fontSize": "36px", "fontWeight": "700", "color": "#0f172a", "marginBottom": "16px"}}, "Trusted by Thousands of Businesses"}, {"id": "testimonials-subheading", "type": "text", "tag": "p", "style": {"fontSize": "18px", "color": "#475569", "lineHeight": "1.6"}}, "Join the growing list of satisfied customers who have transformed their business with our platform."}, {"id": "testimonials-grid", "type": "grid", "tag": "div", "styl